ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Very comprehensive course, which covers all the major topics concerning membrane biology. I would definitely recommend the course.
It is a great survey course for learning about membranes.
Good course that isn't overly demanding of time. I would recommend this course to someone who is interested in membrane biology or who is working on a related topic.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course gave me with a deeper understanding and appreciation for membrane biology. It corrected several misconceptions that I had about membranes. In the end I'm very happy that I took this course.
